Process called "minimum of" that takes a as Integer and b as Integer and c as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Return minimum of three integers
    Let min_ab be minimum with a as a and b as b
    Return minimum with a as min_ab and b as c

Process called "maximum of" that takes a as Integer and b as Integer and c as Integer returns Integer:
